title: DAKINE Eric Pollard Heli Pro Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2012 Eric Pollard Heli Pro Pack:
- Cross and vertical snowboard carry
- Retractable cable ski carry
- Fleece lined goggle pocket
- Deployable water bottle pocket
- Insulated hydro sleeve-
- Quick draw ice axe sleeve
- External snow tool/shovel pocket
- Padded waist belt
